genresAdvancedInfo.name: colombian black metal
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Colombian black metal is a subgenre of heavy metal that originated in Colombia, characterized by its dark and aggressive sound, fast tempos, and harsh vocals. It often incorporates elements of traditional Colombian music and folklore, creating a unique blend of culture and extreme music.
